import { Flex, Spacer, Box } from "@chakra-ui/react"
import Logo from "../atoms/Logo"
import MenuBar from "../atoms/MenuBar"

const Header = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Flex h='70px' bg='red' align='center' justify='center'>
                <Box>
                    <Logo />
                </Box>
                <Box ml='auto'>
                    <MenuBar />
                </Box>
            </Flex>
        </>
    )
}

export default Header
